Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么幸运啊 这不是糟透了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
